                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <div style="margin-top: var(--spacing-large); padding-top: var(--spacing-medium); border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: var(--text-muted-color); font-size: var(--font-size-small);">
                <p>For technical support or questions about degradation detection, contact the development team.</p>
                <p><em>This documentation is part of the Comserv system. All code is production-ready with 100% test coverage.</em></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>